highlights.text: “From The Start” by Laufey is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Hong Kong, up 84 spots at #112.
Anson Lo 盧瀚霆 has the most spots on Top Songs Hong Kong. “Lemonade” is the highest at #2.
“反對無效” by MC 張天賦 has been on Top Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 1575 days straight.
“給千億顆星選中的二人” by 陳卓賢 Ian is the highest new entry on Top Songs Hong Kong at #15.
